00:03:39,210 --> 00:03:40,880
Oh,my God. Rachel Green?
天哪，瑞秋葛林？

51
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:43,170
Rob Tilman!
劳勃提尔曼

52
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:46,580
No, no, it's me. Ross.
不对，是我，罗斯

53
00:03:46,850 --> 00:03:50,050
Oh,I'm sorry. Ross Tilman.
对不起，罗斯提尔曼

54
00:03:51,090 --> 00:03:55,890
-No. No,no. Ross Geller. -Of course! Monica's brother.
-不是，是罗斯盖勒 -对哦，摩妮卡的哥哥

56
00:03:56,130 --> 00:03:58,720
-Yeah. Right. -Wow! How are you?
没错 你好吗？ 

58
00:03:58,970 --> 00:04:00,800
Good. Good. I'm married.
很好，我结婚了

59
00:04:01,270 --> 00:04:02,700
Me too!
我也是

60
00:04:03,610 --> 00:04:06,700
-Isn't it the best? -Oh,it's the best.
结婚真好不是吗？ 就是啊

61
00:04:09,540 --> 00:04:12,950
-So how's Monica? -Really,really great.
摩妮卡好吗？ 非常好

62
00:04:13,210 --> 00:04:17,950
Actually,she's right down the street. You should stop by and say hi.
事实上她就在前面 你应该过去打个招呼

64
00:04:18,220 --> 00:04:20,810
-I would love to. -She'd be so excited.
好啊 她会很高兴

65
00:04:20,990 --> 00:04:21,980
-Okay. -Come on.
好 走吧

66
00:04:22,460 --> 00:04:24,390
Wait,don't you have to pay for...
等等，你不是要买…

67
00:04:24,590 --> 00:04:26,490
Busty Ladies?
“巨乳女O”？

68
00:04:28,930 --> 00:04:33,800
No,that's okay. Some kid asked me to pick it up for him, but I....
没关系，有个小孩托我帮他买 走吧

69
00:04:37,870 --> 00:04:40,570
Don't you have to give him his money back?
你不是应该把钱还给他？

71
00:04:44,110 --> 00:04:46,550
Here you go,buddy. Sorry,no porn for you.
拿去吧，抱歉，你不能看A书

72
00:04:46,710 --> 00:04:48,840
Okay,let's go see Monica.
我们去找摩妮卡吧

73
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:59,150
So,Monica. Still going out with Dr. Boring,huh?
摩妮卡 你还在跟无聊医生交往？

74
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:03,230
He's not boring. He's just...
他才不无聊，他只是…

75
00:05:06,070 --> 00:05:07,090
He's low-key.
只是比较低调

76
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:11,000
-Here you go, one hazelnut latte. -Thank you.
你的榛果拿铁 谢谢

77
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:14,900
You know, the hazelnut, actually not a nut.
其实榛果不是果实

78
00:05:15,180 --> 00:05:17,010
It's a seed.
而是种子

79
00:05:17,850 --> 00:05:19,340
Wow.

80
00:05:20,280 --> 00:05:24,880
Can anyone else name a well-known seed that's been masquerading as a nut?
还有谁能说出一种 假装是果实的常见种子？

81
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:27,610
Oh,dear God. Let me think.
天哪，我想想看

82
00:05:31,130 --> 00:05:32,620
What's the matter?
你怎么了？ 

83
00:05:32,860 --> 00:05:34,290
I got another rejection letter.
我又被退稿了

84
00:05:34,530 --> 00:05:38,120
They said my writing was funny, just not "Archie Comic" funny.
他们说我的东西很有趣 只是不符合“阿奇漫画”风

85
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:41,430
I gotta get back to the hospital.
亲爱的，我得回医院了 

86
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:44,300
-Bye. -Bye-bye.
再见

87
00:05:44,770 --> 00:05:49,110
By the way, the answer is: the Brazil nut.
对了，答案是巴西果

88
00:05:52,810 --> 00:05:55,610
Was his question, "What's more boring than him?"
他的问题比他的人更无趣

89
00:05:56,220 --> 00:05:58,910
And nice sweater vest, by the way.
好帅的毛线背心啊

90
00:05:59,590 --> 00:06:02,520
-Stop it,guys. He's sweet. -Yeah,yeah.
你们别这样，他人很好 是啊

91
00:06:02,690 --> 00:06:05,160
Hey,man. Sorry about the Archie thing.
老兄，退稿的事真可惜 

92
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,950
You need me to give you some money?
你要我给你一些钱吗？

93
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:10,390
I may have no money, but I still have my pride.
我穷归穷，还是有骨气

94
00:06:11,900 --> 00:06:12,890
Really?
是吗？

95
00:06:17,410 --> 00:06:19,530
Joey doesn't have to give you the money.
也许乔伊不必给你钱 

96
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:22,610
-TV stars have assistants,right? -That's an idea.
-电视明星都有助理对吧？-可行喔

97
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:26,010
If I hire an assistant, would you take money from her?
要是我请助理转交 你会收吗？

99
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:29,380
No,Joey. Chandler could be your assistant.
不是啦，钱德可以当你的助理

100
00:06:29,580 --> 00:06:31,750
He could answer all your fan mail and stuff.
他可以帮你回信给影迷

101
00:06:32,020 --> 00:06:34,920
-That would be great! Let's do that! -I could use the money.
-太好了，好主意，就这么办吧 -我有钱领

102
00:06:35,090 --> 00:06:36,180
I'd have time to write.
还有时间写作

103
00:06:36,460 --> 00:06:38,080
-Great. Welcome aboard! -Okay!
漂亮，欢迎加入 感谢

104
00:06:38,290 --> 00:06:40,390
All right. Now,I need to use the bathroom.
我现在要去上厕所 

105
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:43,760
Since I don't need any assistance in there,take a break!
我上厕所不用人帮 你就休息吧 
 
106
00:06:44,030 --> 00:06:45,230
All right.
好

107
00:06:47,570 --> 00:06:48,730
-Hey. -Hey,Phoebe.
菲比，

108
00:06:48,900 --> 00:06:51,630
Guess what. Joey just hired Chandler to be his assistant.
你猜怎样？乔伊找钱德当他的助理

109
00:06:51,870 --> 00:06:53,970
That's so sweet.
真好

110
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,440
Oh! Hang on!
等一下

111
00:06:56,810 --> 00:06:58,570
Hang on!
等我一下

112
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:02,480
Go!
说

113
00:07:03,550 --> 00:07:06,580
No. No,no. I said sell when it hits 50!
不对，不对 我是说一到50点就卖

114
00:07:06,820 --> 00:07:10,420
Five-oh! It's a number! It comes after four-nine!
50是一个数字，在49后面

115
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:14,600
No,it's okay. It's okay. You're allowed one mistake.
没关系，一次错误可以接受

116
00:07:14,830 --> 00:07:16,890
Just kidding. You are,of course,fired.
开玩笑的，你当然被开除了

117
00:07:20,870 --> 00:07:23,740
Oh,what a shame. I really liked her.
真可惜，我很喜欢她

118
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:27,600
Hey,Mon? Mon,look who I ran into!
摩妮卡，你看我遇见谁

119
00:07:27,780 --> 00:07:29,610
Oh,my God,Rachel!
天哪，瑞秋

120
00:07:33,550 --> 00:07:36,350
-God,you look terrific! -So do you!
-你好漂亮 -你也是

121
00:07:38,190 --> 00:07:41,380
-Did you lose weight? -You are so sweet to notice.
-你是不是瘦了？-你居然注意到了 

122
00:07:41,660 --> 00:07:43,180
Yes,I lost 3.5 pounds!
没错，我瘦了3.5磅

123
00:07:46,990 --> 00:07:50,050
You remember my friend Chandler.
记得我的朋友钱德吧

124
00:07:50,330 --> 00:07:52,270
-And that's Phoebe over there. -Hi.
那位是菲比

125
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:56,160
Sit down. How long has it been since we've seen each other?
天哪，快坐下 我们多久没见面了？

126
00:07:56,370 --> 00:07:59,930
1987,the day after Christmas. Sean McMahan's party.
1987年，圣诞节第二天 西恩麦克曼的派对

128
00:08:00,210 --> 00:08:04,670
I played you one of my songs,you know, "lnterplanetary Courtship Ritual."
我弹了我的创作曲给你听 “星际求爱仪式”

129
00:08:06,210 --> 00:08:08,840
Oh,yeah. Right.
喔对

130
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:12,380
-So,now,do you still do music? -Well,sometimes.
-你还在玩音乐吗？ -偶尔

131
00:08:12,590 --> 00:08:15,220
-Come over sometime. I'll play you.. -Oh,my God!
你应该来我家，我弹… 天哪

132
00:08:15,620 --> 00:08:21,030
Joey Tribbiani from Days of Our Lives just walked in here!
“我们的岁月”的 乔伊崔比亚尼刚刚走进来

133
00:08:21,200 --> 00:08:25,890
-Rach,he's a friend of ours. -You're friends with Dr. Drake Ramoray?
-瑞秋，他是我们的朋友 -你们是拉莫瑞医生的朋友？

135
00:08:27,700 --> 00:08:29,430
It's hard to be friends with Drake...
要跟他交朋友有点难 

136
00:08:29,640 --> 00:08:33,370
because of his busy schedule and the fact that he's not real.
因为他很忙，又是个虚构人物

137
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:38,330
Hey,or I could bring my keyboard here sometime.
我也可以把键盘带来

138
00:08:38,580 --> 00:08:40,050
-He's coming over. -Joey?
他过来了 乔伊 

139
00:08:40,250 --> 00:08:41,680
I know. Here,here.
好啦，拿去

141
00:08:43,850 --> 00:08:47,150
No. This is my friend Rachel. We went to high school together.
不是啦，这是我朋友瑞秋 我们是高中同学

142
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:48,980
-Hi. -Hi.

144
00:08:51,860 --> 00:08:53,830
I love you on that show.
我好喜欢你演的戏

145
00:08:54,230 --> 00:08:55,890
I watch you every day.
我每天都看

146
00:08:56,100 --> 00:08:59,090
When you took out your own kidney to save your ex-wife...
你还捐肾救你的前妻…

147
00:08:59,370 --> 00:09:02,060
even though she tried to kill you...
明明知道她想杀你

148
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:04,700
It's always nice to meet fans.
遇见影迷总是很开心

149
00:09:06,210 --> 00:09:08,330
-She's not crazy,is she? -No.
她不会很神经吧？ 不会

150
00:09:08,780 --> 00:09:11,870
So how you doing?
所以…你好吗？

151
00:09:19,290 --> 00:09:20,550
Hang on.
等等…

152
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:24,890
Hang on. Hang on.
等等，等一下

153
00:09:26,030 --> 00:09:27,050
Go!
说

154
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:28,660
Who's this?
谁？

155
00:09:28,900 --> 00:09:30,960
You're gonna like working for me.
好，你要替我工作 

156
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:34,900
What's your name? What kind of name is "Brindy"?
你叫什么名字？ 布伦蒂是什么鸟名字？

158
00:09:37,140 --> 00:09:38,800
Stop talking.
闭嘴

159
00:09:39,470 --> 00:09:42,200
All right, from now on your name is Joan.
好，以后你就叫琼安

160
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:44,700
You can pick your own last name.
姓你自己选

161
00:09:46,510 --> 00:09:49,850
I can't find my pen. Did you eat that too?
我找不到我的笔 也被你吃掉了吗？

162
00:09:51,850 --> 00:09:54,410
-There you are. -Uh-oh,it's my boss.
你在这里 是老板大人

163
00:09:54,990 --> 00:09:57,890
Here's a list of things for you to do today.
这是你今天的工作项目

164
00:09:58,090 --> 00:10:00,360
This is gonna be so great. Thank you so much.
太好了，谢谢你

165
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:04,730
I gotta go to work. I'm delivering twins today, but only one of them is mine.
我要去接生双胞胎了 但只有一个是我的骨肉

166
00:10:09,670 --> 00:10:13,700
"Drop off my dry cleaning. Pick up my vitamins."
把衣服送去干洗 去拿我的维他命

167
00:10:14,340 --> 00:10:16,110
"Teach me how to spell vitamins."
教我怎么写维他命

168
00:10:18,110 --> 00:10:20,210
"Wear in my new jeans."
把我的新牛仔裤穿软

169
00:10:22,050 --> 00:10:24,380
-You realize what you are,don't you? -What?
你知道你的角色吧？什么角色？ 

170
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:26,080
You're his bitch!
你是他的喽罗

171
00:10:27,620 --> 00:10:30,060
No,no! No!
不！不

172
00:10:30,420 --> 00:10:32,860
Wait! You didn't sit on my Kit Kats did you?
你不是压坏了我的巧克力酥吧

173
00:10:33,260 --> 00:10:36,460
No,there was a little, little dip in the market...
不是，市场出了点变化

174
00:10:36,700 --> 00:10:38,690
and I lost 13 million dollars.
我损失了1千3百万

175
00:10:38,900 --> 00:10:40,960
But the Kit Kats are all right?
不过巧克力酥没事吧？

176
00:10:41,900 --> 00:10:44,770
What am I gonna do? I can't call my office, they'll kill me.
怎么办？怎么办？ 通知公司我会被砍死

177
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:48,100
I can't call my clients, they'll kill themselves!
通知客户他们会砍自己

178
00:10:48,380 --> 00:10:51,040
-Great,now my chest hurts. -What?
帅啊，现在又胸口痛 什么？ 

179
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:53,080
My chest hurts.
我的胸口在痛

180
00:10:53,310 --> 00:10:58,410
